function getContrast (   color  ) 

Function getContrast.

get a contrast color to given RGB values for best readability in dependence of background color

Parameters:
color (string) string of hexadecimal color without # sign (length of string is 6 -> red: 2, green: 2, blue 2)
Returns:
color string of the RGB values separated by commas -> ready for use in CSS rgb() function
